%section.setup
  .inner
    %h3 Upload SSH Public Key

    %p
      Before you start an exercise, we need your SSH public key so that we can
      authorize your Git client.

    :markdown
      You can generally find this in `~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub`.

      If you need help setting up your public key, [let us know].

      [let us know]: mailto:learn@thoughtbot.com

  = simple_form_for Gitolite::PublicKey.new do |form|
    = form.input :data
    = form.submit
